Rating: 4
This recipe is fantastic just as written, but I've also made it sans chicken. I usually add a teaspoon or two of cider vinegar to the dressing and spread some thinly sliced pieces of the granny smith apple on top of the salad. Top it off with some freshly ground pepper and it's delightful.

